ercr.ca| publisher =| access-date =27 December 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n\n== Chile==\n* 3rd Mountain Division (''III Division de Monta\u00f1a'')<ref>{{cite web| url =https://www.infodefensa.com/latam/2011/12/22/noticia-el-ejercito-de-chile-crea-la-iii-division-de-montana.html| title =El Ej\u00e9rcito de Chile crea la III Division de Monta\u00f1a| last =| first =| date = | website = infodefensa.com| publisher =| access-date =31 January 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n** 3rd Cavalry Regiment \u201cHussars\u201d (''Regimiento de Caballer\u00eda n.\u00ba 3 \"H\u00fasares\"'')<ref>{{cite web| url =http://www.radiomontecarlosur.cl/el-regimiento-de-caballeria-blindada-no3-husares-celebra-el-mes-de-la-patria/| title =El Regimiento de Caballeria Blindada N\u00ba 3 \"Husares\" Celebra el Mes de la Patria| last =| first =| date = | website = Radio Montecarlo Sur| publisher =| access-date =31 January 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n** 3rd Mountain Detachment \u201cYungay\u201d (''Destacamento de Monta\u00f1a N\u00ba\u00a03 \u201cYungay\u201d'')<ref>{{cite web| url =https://www.infodefensa.com/latam/2018/04/23/noticia-chile-presenta-china-capacidades-tropas-montana.html| title =Chile presenta a China las capacidades de sus tropas de Monta\u00f1a| last =Garcia| first =Nicolas| date = | website = infodefensa.com| publisher =| access-date =31 January 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n***18th Andine Infantry Battalion \u201cOld Guard\u201d (''Batall\u00f3n de Infanter\u00eda Andino N\u00ba 18 \"Guardia Vieja\"'')<ref>{{cite web| url =http://www.elandino.cl/2018/12/10/teniente-coronel-ochoa-es-un-tremendo-orgullo-y-un-gran-desafio-asumir-como-nuevo-comandante/| title =Teniente coronel Ochoa: \u201cEs un tremendo orgullo y un gran desaf\u00edo asumir como nuevo comandante\u201d| last = |first =| date =10 December 2018 | website =el Andino| publisher =| access-date =31 January 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n*** 2nd Mountain Engineers Company \u201cPuente Alto\u201d (''Compa\u00f1\u00eda de Ingenieros de Monta\u00f1a N\