icias/Agrupaci%C3%B3n%20Especial%20de%20Monta%C3%B1a%20particip%C3%B3%20en%20ejercicio%20conjunto%20con%20Fuerzas%20Especiales%20de%20EE.UU.%20-2321| title =AGRUPACI\u00d3N ESPECIAL DE MONTA\u00d1A PARTICIP\u00d3 EN EJERCICIO CONJUNTO CON FUERZAS ESPECIALES DE EE.UU.| last =| first =| date = | website = Ej\u00e9rcito de CHile| publisher =| access-date =31 January 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n\n== China ==\n* [[52nd Mountain Motorized Infantry Brigade (People's Republic of China)|52nd Mountain Combined Arms Brigade]] (''\u5c71\u5730\u5408\u6210\u7b2c52\u65c5 - Sh\u0101nd\u00ec H\u00e9ch\u00e9ng d\u00ec 52 L\u01da'')<ref name=\"ChiMo\">{{cite web| url =https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%96%87%E6%91%98/article/20180824/s00022/1535028268620| title =\u7586\u3001\u85cf\u96b1\u85cf\u5169\u5927\u96c6\u5718\u8ecd \u5f37\u53ef\u6575\u570b| last =| first =| date = 24 August 2018| website = news.mingpao.com| publisher =| access-date =29 November 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n* [[52nd Mountain Motorized Infantry Brigade (People's Republic of China)|53rd Mountain Combined Arms Brigade]] (''\u5c71\u5730\u5408\u6210\u7b2c53\u65c5 - Sh\u0101nd\u00ec H\u00e9ch\u00e9ng d\u00ec 53 L\u01da'')<ref name=\"ChiMo\"/>\n\n== Colombia==\n* 1st High Mountain Battalion \u201cLieutenant Colonel Antonio Arredondo\u201d (''Batall\u00f3n de Alta Monta\u00f1a No.1 \u201cTeniente Coronel  Antonio Arredondo\u201d'')<ref name=\"Log\"> {{cite web| url =https://www.agencialogistica.gov.co/sites/default/files/contracts/migrated/567353/selecci_oacute_n_abreviada_menor_cuant_iacute_a__ley_1150_de_2007__no__015_038_2017_de_2017_contrato_modificatorio_02.pdf| title =CONTRATO MODIFICATORIO No.002| last =| first =| date = | website = agencialogistica.gov.co| publisher =| access-date =4 December 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n* 2nd High Mountain Battalion \u201cGeneral Santos Guti\u00e9rrez Prieto\u201d (''Batall\u00f3n de Alta Monta\u00f1a No.2 \u201cGeneral Santos Guti\u00e9rrez Prieto\u201d'')<ref name=\"Log\"/>\n* 3rd High Mountain Battalion \u201c Rodrigo Lloreda Caicedo (''Batall\u00f3n de Alta Monta\u00f1a No. 3 \"Rodrigo Lloreda Caicedo\"'')<ref name=\"tercera\">{{cite web| url =https://www.ejercito.mil.co/conozcanos/organigrama/unidades_militares/brigadas/239188| title =Tercera Brigada| last =| first =| date = | website = Ej\u00e9rcito Nacional| publisher =| access-date =31 January 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n* 4th High Mountain Battalion \u201cGeneral Benjam\u00edn Herrera Cort\u00e9s\u201d (''Batall\u00f3n de Alta Monta\u00f1a No.4 \u201cGeneral Benjam\u00edn Herrera Cort\u00e9s\u201d'')<ref>{{cite web| url =https://www.ejercito.mil.co/conozcanos/organigrama/unidades_militares/brigadas/240199| title =Vig\u00e9sima Novena Brigada| last =| first =| date = | website = Ej\u00e9rcito Nacional| publisher =| access-date =31 January 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n* 5th High Mountain Battalion \u201cUrbano Castellanos Castillo\u201d (''Batall\u00f3n de Alta Monta\u00f1a No.5 \u201cUrbano Castellanos Castillo\u201d'')<ref>{{cite web| url =https://www.ejercito.mil.co/conozcanos/organigrama/unidades_militares/brigadas/239208| title =Octava Brigada| last =| first =| date = | website = Ej\u00e9rcito Nacional| publisher =| access-date =31 January 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n* 6th High Mountain Battalion \u201cMajor Robinson Daniel Ruiz Garz\u00f3n\u201d (''Batall\u00f3n de Alta Monta\u00f1a No. 6 \"Mayor Robinson Daniel Ruiz Garz\u00f3n\"'')<ref>{{cite web| url =https://www.ejercito.mil.co/conozcanos/organigrama/unidades_militares/brigadas/239187| title =Segunda Brigada| last =| first =| date = | website = Ej\u00e9rcito Nacional| publisher =| access-date =31 January 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n* 7th High Mountain Battalion \u201cMajor Ra\u00fal Guillermo Mahecha Mart\u00ednez\u201d (''Batall\u00f3n de Alta Monta\u00f1a No. 7 \"Mayor Ra\u00fal Guillermo Mahecha Mart\u00ednez\"'')<ref>{{cite web| url =https://www.ejercito.mil.co/conozcanos/organigrama/unidades_militares/brigadas/239210| title =Decima Brigada| last =| 