erv.com|accessdate=27 December 2019}}</ref>\n*[[Royal Navy|Navy]]\n** [[Mountain Leader Training Cadre|Royal Marines Mountain Leader Training Cadre]]<ref >{{cite web|url=http://www.eliteukforces.info/royal-marines/mountain-leaders//|title=Mountain Leaders\n|website=Eliteukforces.info|accessdate=28 January 2019}}</ref>\n\n==United States of America==\n*[[US Army|Army]]\n** [[10th Mountain Division]]\n*** [[86th Infantry Brigade Combat Team|86th Infantry Brigade Combat Team (Mountain) (ARNG) \u201cThe Vermont Brigade\u201d]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://home.army.mil/drum/index.php/units-tenants/86th-IBCT-vermont-NG|title= 86th Infantry Brigade Combat Team, Vermont National Guard |website=home.army.mil}}</ref>\t\n**** [[102nd Infantry Regiment (United States)|1st/102nd Infantry Regiment (Mountain) (Connecticut National Guard)]]\t\n**** [[157th Field Artillery Regiment|1st/157nd Infantry Regiment (Mountain) (Colorado National Guard)]]\t\n**** [[172nd Infantry Regiment (United States)|1st/172nd Infantry Brigade Combat Team (Mountain) (Vermont National Guard)]]\n**[[Army Mountain Warfare School]] (Vermont National Guard)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://rockandice.com/features/mountain-soldiers-army-wwii-today/?cn-reloaded=1|title=The Mountain Soldiers of the U.S. Army: From WWII to Today|website=Rock and Ice}}</ref>\n**Special Forces Advanced Mountain Operations School<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.army.mil/article/80111/special_forces_advanced_mountain_operations_school_announces_course_dates|title=Special Forces Advanced Mountain Operations School announces course dates|website=army.mil}}</ref>\n*[[US Navy|Navy]]\n**[[Mountain Warfare Training Camp Michael Monsoor|Mountain Warfare Training Camp \u201cMichael Monsoor\u201d]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnic.navy.mil/regions/cnrsw/installations/navbase_coronado/about/installations/mountain_warfare_training_camp_michael_monsoor.html/|title=Mountain Warfare Training Camp Michael Monsoor|website=CNIC \u2013 Naval Base Coronado