atribuna.cl/noticia.php?id=MjYzNzI=| title =Destacamento de Monta\u00f1a N\u00ba 17: una reliquia militar en Los \u00c1ngeles | last =Meller| first =Gonzalo| date =5 October 2018 | website = La Tribuna| publisher =| access-date =31 January 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n***17th Mountain Infantry Battalion \u201cTarpellanca\u201d (''Batall\u00f3n de Infanter\u00eda de Monta\u00f1a N\u00ba 17 \"Tarpellanca\"'')<ref>{{cite web| url =https://www.ejercito.cl/noticias/Alto%20nivel%20de%20instrucci%C3%B3n%20del%20Regimiento%20Reforzado%20%20N%C2%B0%2017%20Los%20%C3%81ngeles-1048| title =ALTO NIVEL DE INSTRUCCI\u00d3N DEL REGIMIENTO REFORZADO N\u00b0 17 LOS \u00c1NGELES| last =| first =| date = | website = Ej\u00e9rcito de CHile| publisher =| access-date =31 January 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n*** 3rd Mountain Engineers Company \u201cLos \u00c1ngeles\u201d (''Compa\u00f1\u00eda de Ingenieros de Monta\u00f1a N\u00ba 3 \"Los \u00c1ngeles\"'')<ref>{{cite web| url =https://www.ejercito.cl/noticias/Destacamento%20de%20Monta%C3%B1a%20N%C2%B0%2017%20%E2%80%9CLos%20%C3%81ngeles%E2%80%9D%20finaliz%C3%B3%20apoyo%20en%20Alto%20B%C3%ADo%20B%C3%ADo%20-2197| title =DESTACAMENTO DE MONTA\u00d1A N\u00b0 17 \u201cLOS \u00c1NGELES\u201d FINALIZ\u00d3 APOYO EN ALTO B\u00cdO B\u00cdO| last =| first =| date = | website = Ej\u00e9rcito de Chile| publisher =| access-date =31 January 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n*** 16th Mountain Artillery Battery \u201cCarvallo\u201d (''Bater\u00eda de Artiller\u00eda de Monta\u00f1a N\u00ba 16 \"Carvallo\"'')<ref>{{cite web| url =http://latribuna.cl/noticia.php?id=MTA1ODk=| title =Destacamento de Monta\u00f1a cambi\u00f3 el nombre de la bater\u00eda de artiller\u00eda | last =Diaz| first =Sebastian| date =4 July 2016 | website = La Tribuna| publisher =| access-date =31 January 2019| quote = }}</ref> \n* 20th Divisional Andine Company \"Cochrane\" (''Compa\u00f1\u00eda Andina Divisionaria N\u00b0 20 \"Cochrane\"'')<ref>{{cite web| url =https://www.infodefensa.com/latam/2018/08/2