ain (\"Montagne\")'')<ref>{{cite web| url =https://www.defense.gouv.fr/terre/regiment-par-arme/train/511e-regiment-du-train| title =511e r\u00e9giment du train| last =| first =| date = | website = Defense.gouv.fr| publisher =| access-date =5 February 2020| quote = }}</ref><ref name=\"technicit\u00e9 de haute montagne\">{{cite web| url =https://www.legifrance.gouv.fr/affichTexte.do?cidTexte=JORFTEXT000038316731&categorieLien=id| title = Arr\u00eat\u00e9 du 27 mars 2019 fixant la liste des unit\u00e9s de montagne ouvrant droit \u00e0 la prime de technicit\u00e9 de haute montagne| last =| first =| date = | website = Defense.gouv.fr| publisher =| access-date =5 February 2020| quote = }}</ref>\n* 7th Maintenance Regiment (''7e R\u00e9giment du Mat\u00e9riel'')<ref>{{cite web| url =https://www.defense.gouv.fr/terre/l-armee-de-terre/le-niveau-divisionnaire/commandement-de-la-maintenance-des-forces/7e-regiment-du-materiel| title =7e r\u00e9giment du mat\u00e9riel| last =| first =| date = | website = Defense.gouv.fr| publisher =| access-date =5 February 2020| quote = }}</ref><ref name=\"technicit\u00e9 de haute montagne\"/>\n* Mountain War Conditioning Group (''Groupement d'Aguerrissement Montagne'')<ref>{{cite web| url =https://www.defense.gouv.fr/terre/l-armee-de-terre/le-niveau-divisionnaire/1re-division/groupement-d-aguerrissement-montagne-gam| title =Groupement d'aguerrissement montagne| last =| first =| date = | website = Defense.gouv.fr| publisher =| access-date =4 December 2019| quote = }}</ref> \n** National Mountain War Conditioning Center (''Centre National d'Aguerrissement en Montagne'')\n** Mountain Combat Instruction and Training Center (''Centre d'instruction et d'Entra\u00eenement au Combat en Montagne'')\n\n==Georgia==\n* Mountain Training School \u201cColonel Besik Kutateladze\u201d (''\u10de\u10dd\u10da\u10d9\u10dd\u10d5\u10dc\u10d8\u10d9 \u10d1\u10d4\u10e1\u10d8\u10d9 \u10e5\u10e3\u10d7\u10d0\u10d7\u10d4\u10da\u10d0\u10eb\u10d8\u10e1 \u10e1\u10d0\u10ee\u1