r/start/dienstst/10pzdiv/gldg/gebjgbrig23/gldg/gebjgbtl232/| title =Gebirgsj\u00e4gerbataillon 232 in Bischofswiesen| last =| first =| date = | website = deutschesheer.de| publisher =| access-date =31 January 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n** 233rd Mountain Light Infantry Battalion (''Gebirgsj\u00e4gerbataillon 233'')<ref>{{cite web| url =https://www.deutschesheer.de/portal/a/heer/start/dienstst/10pzdiv/gldg/gebjgbrig23/gldg/gebjgbtl233/| title =Gebirgsj\u00e4gerbataillon 233 in Mittenwald| last =| first =| date = | website = deutschesheer.de| publisher =| access-date =31 January 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n** 8th Mountain Supply Battalion (''Gebirgsversorgungsbataillon 8'')<ref>{{cite web| url =https://www.deutschesheer.de/portal/a/heer/start/dienstst/10pzdiv/gldg/gebjgbrig23/gldg/gebversbtl8/| title =Gebirgsversorgungsbataillon 8 in F\u00fcssen| last =| first =| date = | website = deutschesheer.de| publisher =| access-date =31 January 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n** 8th Mountain Engineers Battalion (''Gebirgspionierbataillon 8'')<ref>{{cite web| url =https://www.deutschesheer.de/portal/a/heer/start/dienstst/10pzdiv/gldg/gebjgbrig23/gldg/gebpibtl8/| title =Gebirgspionierbataillon 8 in Ingolstadt| last =| first =| date = | website = deutschesheer.de| publisher =| access-date =31 January 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n** 230th Operations and Training Center for Pack Animals (''Einsatz- und Ausbildungszentrum f\u00fcr Tragtierwesen 230'')<ref>{{cite web| url =https://www.deutschesheer.de/portal/a/heer/start/dienstst/10pzdiv/gldg/gebjgbrig23/gldg/einsausbzgebtrgtwes230/| title =Einsatz- und Ausbildungszentrum f\u00fcr Tragtierwesen 230 in Bad Reichenhall| last =| first =| date = | website = deutschesheer.de| publisher =| access-date =31 January 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n* Mountain and Winter Warfare Training Support Point (''Ausbildungsst\u00fctzpunkt Gebirgs- und Winterkamp'')<ref>{{cite web| url =https://www.deutschesheer.de/portal/a/heer/start/dienstst/ausbkdo/ausbeinrichtungen/ausbzinf/gliederung/| title =Gliederung des Ausbildungszentrums Infanterie| last =| first =| date = | website = deutschesheer.de| publisher =| access-date =31 January 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n\n==Greece==\n* Mountain Commandos Company (''\u039b\u03cc\u03c7\u03bf\u03c2 \u039f\u03c1\u03b5\u03b9\u03bd\u03ce\u03bd \u039a\u03b1\u03c4\u03b1\u03b4\u03c1\u03bf\u03bc\u03ce\u03bd'')<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.news247.gr/koinonia/fotografies-etsi-ekpaideyontai-oi-ellines-katadromeis-tis-mayris-moiras-sta-chionia.6490773.html|title=\u03a6\u03c9\u03c4\u03bf\u03b3\u03c1\u03b1\u03c6\u03af\u03b5\u03c2: \u0388\u03c4\u03c3\u03b9 \u03b5\u03ba\u03c0\u03b1\u03b9\u03b4\u03b5\u03cd\u03bf\u03bd\u03c4\u03b1\u03b9 \u03bf\u03b9 \u0388\u03bb\u03bb\u03b7\u03bd\u03b5\u03c2 \u03ba\u03b1\u03c4\u03b1\u03b4\u03c1\u03bf\u03bc\u03b5\u03af\u03c2 \u03c4\u03b7\u03c2 \u039c\u03b1\u03cd\u03c1\u03b7\u03c2 \u039c\u03bf\u03af\u03c1\u03b1\u03c2 \u03c3\u03c4\u03b1 \u03c7\u03b9\u03cc\u03bd\u03b9\u03b1|website=News 24/7|access-date=24 December 2019}}</ref>\n* Mountain Training Center for Ski Warfare (''\u039a\u03ad\u03bd\u03c4\u03c1\u03bf \u0395\u03ba\u03c0\u03b1\u03af\u03b4\u03b5\u03c5\u03c3\u03b7\u03c2 \u039f\u03c1\u03b5\u03b9\u03bd\u03bf\u03cd \u0391\u03b3\u03ce\u03bd\u03b1 \u03a7\u03b9\u03bf\u03bd\u03bf\u03b4\u03c1\u03cc\u03bc\u03c9\u03bd - K\u00e9ntro Ekpaideisis Oreino\u00fa Ag\u00f3na Chionodr\u00f3mon'')<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.armynow.net/keoax-mathtes-episkefthkan-xionodromoys-olympo-fvto/|title=\u039a\u0395\u039f\u0391\u03a7: \u039c\u03b1\u03b8\u03b7\u03c4\u03ad\u03c2 \u03b5\u03c0\u03b9\u03c3\u03ba\u03ad\u03c6\u03b8\u03b7\u03ba\u03b1\u03bd \u03c4\u03bf\u03c5 \u03a7\u03b9\u03bf\u03bd\u03bf\u03b4\u03c1\u03cc\u03bc\u03bf\u03c5\u03c2 \u03c3\u03c4\u03bf\u03bd \u038c\u03bb\u03c5\u03bc\u03c0\u03bf|website=armynow.net}}</ref>\n\n==Guatemala==\n* Mountain Operations Brigade (''Brigada de Operaciones para Monta\u00f1a'')<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mindef.mil.gt/Organizacion/3fuerzas_aire_mar_tierra/fuerza_tierra/c/c8/c8_historia.html|title=Historia Brigada de Operaciones para Monta\u00f1a|website=Mindef.mil.gt|accessdate=22 November 2019}}</ref> \n** Mountain Infantry Battalion (''Batall\u00f3n de Infanter\u00eda de Monta\u00f1a'')\n** Mountain Reconnaissance Company (''Compa\u00f1\u00eda de Reconocimiento de Monta\u00f1a'')\n\n== India==\n[[File:Yudh Abhyas 2013 (1).JPG|thumb|right|Gurkha troops of India's 99th Mountain Brigade]]\n* [[III Corps (India)|III Mountain Corps]] <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.jagranjosh.com/general-knowledge/basic-structure-and-commands-of-indian-army-1502284025-1l|title=What is the Structure and Commands of Indian Army|website=Jagran Josh|accessdate=2 February 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/india/divisions.htm|title=Indian Army Divisions|website=globalsecurity.org|accessdate=10 October 2019}}</ref>\n** [[2nd Infantry Division (India)|2nd Mountain Infantry Division]] (''2 \u0935\u093e \u0921\u094b\u0902\u0917\u0930\u0940 \u092a\u093e\u092f\u0926\u0933 \u0935\u093f\u092d\u093e\u0917 - 2 V\u0101 D\u014d\u1e45gar\u012b P\u0101yada\u1e37a Vibh\u0101ga'')<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/india/2-div.htm|title=2 Mountain Division|last=Pike|first=John|website=www.globalsecurity.org|access-date=2017-05-14}}</ref>\n** 56th Mountain Infantry Division (''56 \u0935\u093e \u0921\u094b\u0902\u0917\u0930\u0940 \u092a\u093e\u092f\u0926\u0933 \u0935\u093f\u092d\u093e\u0917 - 56 V\u0101 D\u014d\u1e45gar\u012b P\u0101yada\u1e37a Vibh\u0101ga'')<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.chindits.co.in/2009/11/armys-first-mountain-division-for-china.html|title=Army's first mountain division for China in northeast kicks off !!|date=11 November 2009|publisher=Chindits|language=en|access-date=12 October 2018}}</ref>\n** 57th Mountain Infantry Division (''57 \u0935\u093e \u0921\u094b\u0902\u0917\u0930\u0940 \u092a\u093e\u092f\u0926\u0933 \u0935\u093f\u092d\u093e\u0917 - 57 V\u0101 D\u014d\u1e45gar\u