hita.ro/brigada-61-vanatori-de-munte-general-virgil-badulescu-are-un-nou-comandant| title =Brigada 61 V\u00e2n\u0103tori de Munte \u201eGeneral Virgil B\u0103dulescu\u201d are un nou comandant| last =| first =| date = 12 December 2017 | website = ZiarHarghita.ro| publisher =| access-date =1 February 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n** 17th Mountain Light Infantry Battalion \u201cVoivode Drago\u0219\u201d (''Batalionul 17 V\u00e2n\u0103tori de Munte \u201cDrago\u0219 Vod\u0103\u201d '')<ref>{{cite web| url =https://ziarharghita.ro/trecere-in-rezerva-la-batalionul-17-vanatori-de-munte| title =Trecere \u00een rezerv\u0103 la Batalionul 17 V\u00e2n\u0103tori de Munte| last =| first =| date = 12 February 2018| website = ZiarHarghita.ro| publisher =| access-date =1 February 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n** 22nd Mountain Light Infantry Battalion \u201cCire\u0219oa\u201d (''Batalionul 22 V\u00e2n\u0103tori de Munte \u201cCire\u0219oaia\u201d'')<ref>{{cite web| url =https://ziarharghita.ro/batalionul-22-vanatori-de-munte-ciresoaia-in-ascensiune-pe-acoperisul-romaniei| title =Batalionul 22 V\u00e2n\u0103tori de munte \u201d Cire\u0219oaia \u201e, \u00een ascensiune pe acoperi\u0219ul Rom\u00e2niei| last =| first =| date = 2 November 2017| website = ZiarHarghita.ro| publisher =| access-date =1 February 2019| quote = }}</ref> \n** 24th Mountain Light Infantry Battalion \u201cGeneral Gheorghe Avramescu\u201d (''Batalionul 24 V\u00e2n\u0103tori de Munte\"General Gheorghe Avramescu\u201d'')<ref>{{cite web| url =https://ziarharghita.ro/schimbare-de-comanda-la-batalionul-24-vanatori-de-munte-general-gheorghe-avramescu| title =Schimbare de comand\u0103 la Batalionul 24 V\u00e2n\u0103tori de Munte \u201e General Gheorghe Avramescu \u201d| last =| first =| date = 20 October 2017| website = ZiarHarghita.ro| publisher =| access-date =1 February 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n** 385th Artillery Battalion \u201cIancu de Hunedoara\u201d (''Divizionul 385 Artilerie \u201cIancu de Hunedoara\u201d'')<ref>{{cite web