zsu/128-girsko-pihotna-brygada-zsu/| title =128 \u043e\u043a\u0440\u0435\u043c\u0430 \u0433\u0456\u0440\u0441\u044c\u043a\u043e-\u0448\u0442\u0443\u0440\u043c\u043e\u0432\u0430 \u0417\u0430\u043a\u0430\u0440\u043f\u0430\u0442\u0441\u044c\u043a\u0430 \u0431\u0440\u0438\u0433\u0430\u0434\u0430| last =| first =| date = 13 January 2016 | website = kapterka.com.ua| publisher =| access-date =5 November 2019| quote = }}</ref>\n** 15th Independent Mountain Assault Battalion ('''15-\u0456\u0439 \u043e\u043a\u0440\u0435\u043c\u0438\u043c \u0433\u0456\u0440\u0441\u044c\u043a\u043e-\u0448\u0442\u0443\u0440\u043c\u043e\u0432\u0438\u043c \u0431\u0430\u0442\u0430\u043b\u044c\u0439\u043e\u043d\u0430\u043c - 15-iy Okremym Hirs\u02b9ko-Shturmovym Batal\u02b9yonam'')\n\n==United Kingdom==\n*[[British Army|Army]]\n** Mountain Troops, [[22 Special Air Service Regiment]]<ref >{{cite web|url=http://www.eliteukforces.info/special-air-service/mountain-troop//|title=Special Air Service (SAS) - Mountain Troop|website=Eliteukforces.info|accessdate=28 January 2019}}</ref>\n** Joint Service Mountain Training Centre<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.govserv.org/XX/Unknown/361761547168667/Joint-Service-Mountain-Training-Centre-%28JSMTC%29|title=JOINT SERVICE MOUNTAIN TRAINING CENTRE (JSMTC)|website=govserv.com|accessdate=27 December 2019}}</ref>\n*[[Royal Navy|Navy]]\n** [[Mountain Leader Training Cadre|Royal Marines Mountain Leader Training Cadre]]<ref >{{cite web|url=http://www.eliteukforces.info/royal-marines/mountain-leaders//|title=Mountain Leaders\n|website=Eliteukforces.info|accessdate=28 January 2019}}</ref>\n\n==United States of America==\n*[[US Army|Army]]\n** [[10th Mountain Division]]\n*** [[86th Infantry Brigade Combat Team|86th Infantry Brigade Combat Team (Mountain) (ARNG) \u201cThe Vermont Brigade\u201d]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://home.army.mil/drum/index.php/units-tenants/86th-IBCT-vermont-NG|title= 86th Infantry Brigade Combat Team, Vermont National Guard |website=home.army.mil}}</